values: Second day with out seeing trevor, my walmart mission yesterday was greatly accomplished! W0o0T! I have to work tonight, but I think before I go, I'm going to go on an extremely LONG walk by myself, I'm slowly getting depressed and I dont know why.. I feel like a blob of skin filled with vital organs! >.<! I have a test in math today, I actually did my home work, in hopes of bringing up my grade! on a different note, before second period, I found out one of my best friends, since like my freshman year, was gay...! ARG, I cant stand not being able to see trevor, I cried myself to sleep last night, I miss him so much! Hopefully when he gets back we can spend more time together, like we dont already, psh! anyways, my tum tum tummy hurts!

Today is the first day that I havent seen Trevor, 5 more to go! I dread going to 4th period, knowing he wont be there to give me little glances and winks and kisses in the air... AHHH! I'm slowly starting to think that I'm obsessed..? I'm going today after school to get my pictures developed of me, Trevor and random objects and people! WOOT! Todays my last day off of work, I have to friggen work everyday until Tuesday, then we get the next schedule! Hopefully I'll make some money this weekend, last saturday I worked a 7 hr. shift and only got $13 but, we were also very very slow! Anyways, off to explore more pages! AND I'M OFF!

this weekend has been, interesting... Friday, Trevor, Zack, and I went to Randy's to get my stuff and he was in his room with some girl named Brandy! YUCK and YUCK! He started crap and it was DUMB! But after we listened to "angry" music, it was all better! We went downtown, in hopes of finding something to DO! >.<! Saturday morning I hung out with Trevor, but I had to babysit that night! >.< again! Sunday, I had to be home at 5, but it worked out, Kailee stayed the night.. I went to get trevor and we spent the day together and we went to the beach! <3! It was so.. sweet, but I had to take him to his sisters house =(! POOPI! Come Monday morning, I had this huge guilt trip and I had to tell my Mawmaw the real reason I broke up with Randy, him always wanting sex, she didnt flip out as much as I thought she would, Randy was a mistake and if I could take it back I would! But yesterday I did get to move the day bed in my room, FINALLY MORE ROOM FOR A NEW BOOKSHELF! Trevor's going out of town tomorrow, *SIGH*, for 6 effin days, I dont know how I'm going to stand not being able to see him, I'll go into like DTs or something, but he promised to call everynight! ANYWHO, I have work tonight, which should be interesting! I'm off to find a reason to press the number 5, wait I just did, I'm off to find a reason to type the correct spelling of the number 5!

I'm currently sitting in the library! School so far hasn't been that bad, I had my favorite sub. in english, Mr. Mallone! He's really into Ginsberg and Faulkner! YAY! He's an ENGLISH MAJOR! *DROOLS* MY FUTURE CAREER RELIES ON ENGLISH! Anywho, about my, erm, journal entry title, theres a pep-rally today, that I will be skipping with Trevor and Zach, well, possibly Zach! But yeah, were going to Randy's after work to get my stuff, I hope he's not there!!! erm, were going downtown after that! YAY! and to my secret cafe! WOOT! well, I shall be headed to go play online video games!! CHOW for NOW!

Growing up is such a hassle why can't we stay young forever and be in denial? I got wrote up today for hugging Trevor which I think is BS, but we have detention together, always a plus! In the library with Amber, skipping lunch, I hate the whole lets be as loud as possible thing so we can give people headaches! GRR! I'm dreading 4th period, more idiots (except Trevor) and ALG 2/ Trig! OH NO! OFF to HELL I go!

YO, sorry I havent updated in a while I've been busy like whoa out the ass! Well Xander hasnt called me, I'm starting to think that he's angered at me...but oh well, on Thursday, I met Randy at Marsha's Menagerie and Mike, Chris, Him and I dressed up, hehehe, and we went to McDonalds and had a ketchup fight and I went into the bathroom and scared Randy, then like out of no where we started kissing, it was gross... LOL! But we went back to his house afterwards and I got to meet his mother and we went to the grocery store and dropped Chris off and then we went to the Grind and it was cold so we went to Starbucks and we shot some pool, Randy and I against Mike...hehehe...Randy and I make a PERFECT team! But we went back to the Grind and went to the movies and saw I,Robot, it was dumb! But anyways, it was aroud 11 so Mike took me back home and I cleaned my room and went to sleep! I'm glad Randy called Thursday in, I had a blast with him and Mike! Mike felt kind of bad, but I still had fun and I think he did too! Randy and I started dating officially July 24, at 1:40am! HEHEHE! He had to go to work today, bummer, but I do too... BLAH! DaMN WAFFLE HOUSE!!!! But he's gonna call me after he gets off at 4 and before I go to work at 5! well I have to finish babysitting! 

I LOVE RANDY
MY ONE AND ONLY LOVE MUFFIN~

Shelbster!

Sorry I havent updated... but this past weekend was so kickass! Kailee and I went down to Panama City! WOOT! Friday morning we left adn went to our other house.. packed a cooler and left for the beach.. we went to these neat shops called the joint, beatniks, and purple haze... We got some neat tapeistries and wraps... and I got a neat bandana, its green =)! We went home early friday night so we could remember how to get back. Satuday we went back to the beach and walked around, we got some floats and floated out into the water.. hehehee, after night fall we hit the strip and rode down it a few times and yelled and had a great time! After we rode down the strip, we went back to the beach with Kailee's acoustic and sat on a picnic table.. she played and I danced... hehee, we met some sad kid who walked by us like 4 times.. he was weird.. and we met some drunk guys who stayed in a condo next to the beach, they wanted us to play, but we were on our way back to the car..lol.. so we went home and play SPANISH GOLDFISH!!! LOL!! Tienes ocho, NO, GOOOFEESH! LOL! But on Sunday we got back up and went to dun dun dun WAFFLE HOUSE.. OMG you'd think on our days off from there, we wouldnt be caught dead there! anywho, we went to waffle house then to walmart, we played around and then once again went back to the beach... hehehe.. we went to tropical smoothie too!!! YUMM! but we came back home! SLEPT and unpacked! I had work on monday and yesterday! BLAH! I beat up David Vanwhy.. last night... hehehee! Anyways, today I was going to try and get frankie shots, but I cant figure out the vets number, its NOT even IN the PHONE BOOK! WTF?!? But I'm going to the gym in a bit... 
until next time kids
shelbster

AHHHH!I talked to david (miami) until about 1, then I talked to chris (nav) (gees there are alot of people with those names) until 5ish... and I finally conked out at like 6.. so YEAH, I hope I dont have to work tonight! UHM, a little update, I got a new kitty, from jacks house, his names francious, but we call him frankie... hes like 8 weeks old and erm, kailee and i are going to panama city this weekend to hang out at the beach, check out some venues and cafes... maybe shows?!?! were staying the weekend... at the other house we have.. FUN! I've been working alot lately.. BLAH! the ICK smell of awful waffle on my clothes makes me cringe now.. I worked with David Vanywhy monday and hes dating ashley (another waitress) I felt kind of bad... but oh well.
